{"tid":2125903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國駐成都總領館門口徽標晚上開始拆除   美國外交官被要求在30天內離開中國","createTime":"2020-07-26T13:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T14:37:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"39fcf072130c3b71fc439e000cd88d65841b2939","tid":2125903,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539994-20200726.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539994-20200726.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=9a61e021\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539994-20200726.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=07ce8d25\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539994-20200726.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中方要求關閉美國駐成都總領事館的限期據報明天上午屆滿，內地傳媒報道，領事館晚上開始拆除門口徽標，館內車輛陸續駛出。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述知情人士報道，領事館的美國外交官被要求在30天內離開中國。<br />\n<br />\n領事館外保安嚴密，有公安駐守，一架巴士朝早由領事館駛走，附近街道就連續第二日吸引大批民眾停留拍照或錄影。較早時有內地傳媒發放照片見到，有外籍人員從領事館攜帶行李自行離開。"},{"pid":"5fdc22f63e7a08750f066982e4658968d084498e","tid":2125903,"uid":156652,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PsDQp5q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsDQp5q.gif&h=6419f127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4df53cc64d1f19c7cc0c16e0cd21cc93f22e9fe0","tid":2125903,"uid":146285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"美國駐成都總領館是美國的國家財產。根據《維也納領事關係公約》，中方不得以任何方式侵犯美國駐成都總領館。"},{"pid":"e0eb6ffd8099f521f595beea4c13418c570e2b5e","tid":2125903,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">領事館的美國外交官被要求在30天內離開中國</span></blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Kev9zL.gif\"